text: Cotycicuiara latifascia is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 2008. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Cotycicuiara latifascia. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2008
